        biochar_desc: { en: `Biochar production using locally-fabricated Kon-Tiki kilns. Transforms agricultural waste into stable soil carbon. Applied to farms across Kabazana A&B, Misiera, and Kigali village as part of REGESOIL integrated soil regeneration system.`, fr: `Production de biochar a l'aide de fours Kon-Tiki fabriques localement. Transforme les dechets agricoles en carbone stable pour le sol. Applique aux fermes de Kabazana A et B, Misiera et du village de Kigali dans le cadre du systeme integre de regeneration des sols REGESOIL.`, sw: `Uzalishaji wa biochar kwa kutumia tanuru za Kon-Tiki zilizoundwa hapa. Hubadilisha taka za kilimo kuwa kaboni imara ya udongo. Inatumiwa kwenye mashamba ya Kabazana A na B, Misiera, na kijiji cha Kigali kama sehemu ya mfumo wa REGESOIL wa kuzaliwa upya kwa udongo.`, rw: `Gukora biochar hakoreshejwe imifuka ya Kon-Tiki yakozwe mu gace. Ihindura imyanda y'ubuhinzi ibe karubone ihamye y'ubutaka. Ikoreshwa mu mirima ya Kabazana A na B, Misiera, no mu mudugudu wa Kigali nk'igice cy'uruhererekane rwa REGESOIL rwo gusubiza ubutaka.` },
