        regesoil_outcome2: { en: `Soil drainage improved 40% (10 cm/hour to 6.5 cm/hour)`, fr: `Drainage du sol ameliore de 40% (10 cm/heure a 6,5 cm/heure)`, sw: `Mifereji ya udongo imeboreshwa kwa 40% (cm 10/saa hadi cm 6.5/saa)`, rw: `Imifereji y'ubutaka yaboshye 40% (cm 10/isaha kugeza cm 6.5/isaha)` },
        regesoil_outcome3: { en: `4 food forest demonstration sites across Kabazana A&B, Kigali village`, fr: `4 sites de demonstration de forets comestibles dans les zones Kabazana A et B, village de Kigali`, sw: `Maeneo 4 ya maonyesho ya misitu ya chakula katika Kabazana A na B, kijiji cha Kigali`, rw: `Ahantu 4 h'ibirego by'amashyamba y'ibiribwa mu Kabazana A na B, umudugudu wa Kigali` },
        regesoil_outcome4: { en: `340 farmers adopted food forest methods (68% of 500 target)`, fr: `340 agriculteurs ont adopte les methodes de forets comestibles (68% de l'objectif de 500)`, sw: `Wakulima 340 walipitisha mbinu za msitu wa chakula (68% ya lengo la 500)`, rw: `Abahinzi 340 bakoresheje uburyo bw'amashyamba y'ibiribwa (68% y'intego ya 500)` },
        womens_label: { en: `Economic Independence - 2018-Present - Led by Maria Antoine`, fr: `Independance Economique - 2018-Present - Dirige par Maria Antoine`, sw: `Uhuru wa Kiuchumi - 2018-Sasa - Inaoongozwa na Maria Antoine`, rw: `Ubwigenge bw'Ubukungu - 2018-Ubu - Iyobowe na Maria Antoine` },
        womens_title: { en: `Women's Empowerment`, fr: `Autonomisation des Femmes`, sw: `Uwezeshaji wa Wanawake`, rw: `Guha Abagore Imbaraga` },
        womens_desc1: { en: `We have trained nearly 700 women with entrepreneurial skills and are helping them play active roles in greening the settlement by planting moringa and other fruit trees while building small businesses.`, fr: `Nous avons forme pres de 700 femmes avec des competences entrepreneuriales et les aidons a jouer des roles actifs dans le verdissement du camp en plantant de la moringa et d'autres arbres fruitiers tout en developpant de petites entreprises.`, sw: `Tumefunza karibu wanawake 700 ujuzi wa ujasiriamali na tunawaasaidia kucheza majukumu ya kazi katika kuimarisha makazi kwa kupanda moringa na miti mingine ya matunda wakati wakijenga biashara ndogo.`, rw: `Twatojwe hafi abagore 700 ubushobozi bw'ubucuruzi kandi tubafasha kugira uruhare rw'ingenzi mu guteza imbere uburaro bwo gutera moringa n'ibiti by'imbuto bindi bashaka no gushyiraho amasosiyeti amato.` },
        womens_desc2: { en: `Women use moringa tree leaves to make organic and liquid soaps, enabling them to generate sustainable incomes. In combination with teaching soap making, we also offer business training and networking opportunities.`, fr: `Les femmes utilisent les feuilles de l'arbre moringa pour fabriquer des savons biologiques et liquides, leur permettant de generer des revenus durables. En plus de l'enseignement de la fabrication de savon, nous offrons egalement une formation commerciale et des opportunites de reseautage.`, sw: `Wanawake wanatumia majani ya mti wa moringa kutengeneza sabuni za kikaboni na kioevu, kuwawezesha kuzalisha mapato endelevu. Pamoja na kufundisha utengenezaji wa sabuni, pia tunatoa mafunzo ya biashara na fursa za mtandao.`, rw: `Abagore bakoresha amababi y'igiti cya moringa gukora isabune kama no rurimi, bibahatira gushaka amafaranga arama. Hamwe no kwigisha gukora isabune, natwe dutanga amahugurwa y'ubucuruzi n'amahirwe yo guhuza.` },
        womens_programs_heading: { en: `Programs Include:`, fr: `Les Programmes Comprennent :`, sw: `Programu Zinajumuisha:`, rw: `Porogaramu Zirimo:` },
        womens_program1: { en: `Organic soap making`, fr: `Fabrication de savon biologique`, sw: `Utengenezaji wa sabuni asilia`, rw: `Gukora isabune kama` },
        womens_program2: { en: `Mushroom cultivation`, fr: `Culture de champignons`, sw: `Ukuzaji wa uyoga`, rw: `Gutera ibihumyo` },
        womens_program3: { en: `Moringa tree planting`, fr: `Plantation d'arbres moringa`, sw: `Upandaji wa mti wa moringa`, rw: `Gutera ibiti bya moringa` },
        womens_program4: { en: `Business skills training`, fr: `Formation aux competences commerciales`, sw: `Mafunzo ya ujuzi wa biashara`, rw: `Amahugurwa y'ubushobozi bw'ubucuruzi` },
        womens_program5: { en: `Networking opportunities`, fr: `Opportunites de reseautage`, sw: `Fursa za mtandao`, rw: `Amahirwe yo guhuza` },
        regen_label: { en: `Core Approach - 2018-Present - Led by Paulinho Muzaliwa`, fr: `Approche Centrale - 2018-Present - Dirige par Paulinho Muzaliwa`, sw: `Mbinu ya Msingi - 2018-Sasa - Inaoongozwa na Paulinho Muzaliwa`, rw: `Inzira y'Ingenzi - 2018-Ubu - Iyobowe na Paulinho Muzaliwa` },
        regen_desc1: { en: `Regenerative agriculture is a holistic approach where we involve all the elements to reach the optimum impact, which means activating the farmers while teaching them how to regenerate the soil.`, fr: `L'agriculture regenerative est une approche holistique ou nous impliquons tous les elements pour atteindre un impact optimal, ce qui signifie activer les agriculteurs tout en leur apprenant a regenerer le sol.`, sw: `Kilimo cha kuzaliwa upya ni mbinu ya jumla ambapo tunahusisha vipengele vyote kufikia athari bora, ambayo inamaanisha kuwezesha wakulima wakati wa kuwafundisha jinsi ya kufufua udongo.`, rw: `Ubuhinzi buzasubiranya ni inzira y'imbonane aho duhuza ibintu byose kugira ngo tugerehe ingaruka ziza cyane, bivuze guha abahinzi imbaraga nk'uko tubigisha uburyo bwo gusubiza ubutaka.` },
        regen_desc2: { en: `For decades, people have been using chemical fertilizers, harming the soil and people's health. We believe that with worm compost, biochar, and diverse planting, we can regenerate soils, improving water conservation, remineralization, soil structure, and microlife, while inspiring optimism and hope.`, fr: `Depuis des decennies, les gens utilisent des engrais chimiques, nuisant au sol et a la sante des personnes. Nous croyons qu'avec le compost de vers, le biochar et les plantations diversifiees, nous pouvons regenerer les sols, ameliorant la conservation de l'eau, la remineralisation, la structure du sol et la microflore, tout en inspirant optimisme et espoir.`, sw: `Kwa miongo mingi, watu wamekuwa wakitumia mbolea za kemikali, kudhuru udongo na afya ya watu. Tunaamini kwamba kwa mbolea ya minyoo, biochar, na kupanda mbalimbali, tunaweza kufufua udongo, kuboresha uhifadhi wa maji, remineralization, muundo wa udongo, na microlife, huku ukichochea matumaini na tumaini.`, rw: `Mu bihe byinshi, abantu bakoresha ifumbire ry'imiti, bishimirira ubutaka n'ubuzima bw'abantu. Twemera ko n'ifumbire ry'inzoka, biochar, no gutera ibintu bitandukanye, dushobora gusubiza ubutaka, gukomeza kubika amazi, gusubiza imyunyu ngugu, imiterere y'ubutaka, n'ubuzima buto, ndetse no gushyigikira ibyiringiro n'icyizere.` },
        regen_desc3: { en: `We are shifting from dependency on organizations like the World Food Program by taking care of the soil through organic amendments and planting trees to mitigate micro-climate changes.`, fr: `Nous nous eloignons de la dependance envers des organisations comme le Programme alimentaire mondial en prenant soin du sol grace a des amendements organiques et en plantant des arbres pour attenuer les changements microclimatiques.`, sw: `Tunahamia kutoka kwa utegemezi kwa mashirika kama Programu ya Chakula Duniani kwa kutunza udongo kupitia marekebisho ya kikaboni na kupanda miti kupunguza mabadiliko ya hali ya hewa ndogo.`, rw: `Turiyimura mu gutegemera imiryango nk'Porogaramu y'Ibiribwa by'Isi yose binyuze mu kwitaho ubutaka binyuze mu iyongerera ry'ibikaboni no gutera ibiti kugabanya impinduka z'ibihe bito.` },
