            rn: "Umuryango uyobowe n'impunzi watsindiye ibihembo muri Nakivale, Ubugande. Wemejwe na UNHCR, Ockenden International, na Lush Spring Prize. Kuva 2018: twatoje abahinzi 3,000+ mu gushushanya amashyamba y'ibiribwa, gukora imyanda y'ibiribwa 800 kg ku cyumweru tuyihindura ifumbire ry'inzoka, kwigisha abagore 700 guhinga ibihumyo n'isabune kama.",
